verse.lines:
{lang-eng}There is a safe and secret place,
Beneath the wings Divine,
Reserved for all the heirs of grace;
O be that refuge mine!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}The least and feeblest there may bide,
Uninjured and unawed;
While thousands fall on every side
He rests secure in God.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}He feeds in pastures, large and fair,
Of love and truth Divine;
O child of God, O glory's heir,
How rich a lot is thine.{/lang-eng}
